### Travel API Tests

### Create Travel
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Travel
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "رحلة عمل إلى دبي",
  "destination": "دبي، الإمارات العربية المتحدة",
  "purpose": "مؤتمر تقني واجتماعات عمل",
  "startDate": "2024-03-15T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2024-03-20T00:00:00Z",
  "transportMode": "طائرة",
  "accommodation": "فندق برج العرب"
}

### Get All Travels
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Travel?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Travels with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Travel?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&search=دبي
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Travels by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Travel?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&from=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2024-12-31T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Travels by Destination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Travel?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&destination=دبي
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Travel by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Travel/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Travel
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/Travel/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "رحلة عمل محدثة إلى دبي",
  "destination": "دبي، الإمارات العربية المتحدة",
  "purpose": "مؤتمر تقني واجتماعات عمل محدثة",
  "startDate": "2024-03-16T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2024-03-21T00:00:00Z",
  "transportMode": "طائرة",
  "accommodation": "فندق برج الخليفة"
}

### Delete Travel
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Travel/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
